textBeforeTable: Admission is free to the public. The Oklahoma State men and the Iowa State women were crowned the 2011 Big 12 Cross Country Champions. The victory Cowboys marked their fourth consecutive Big 12 Championship. The top men's and women's teams are crowned league champion, while the top 15 individuals in each race are named all-conference. The 2012 Big 12 Cross Country Championships will be held on Saturday, Oct. 27, in Austin, Texas at the Jimmy Clay Golf Course. The University of Texas will host the event for the second time. UT last hosted the event in 2003.
